  m_text: You've accidentally turned into a cat and now you have to make a potion
    that will turn you back into a human! Unfortunately, you don't have all the ingredients
    you need, nor the recipe! Time to experiment with combinations, brew potions,
    and trade customers for rare ingredients. But be careful! Once you brew your
    potion, you can't get those ingredients back! If you get stuck, the recipe book
    records all potions you've brewed and has some helpful hints. Good luck and happy
    brewing!
